data.meta_description: Following singles such as “Backseat” with Project Pat, as well as “Pop That Trunk,” Juicy J and Wiz Khalifa’s brand new collaborative project Stoner’s Night has finally been unveiled in full. Masterfully combining the two veterans’ respective styles, the 13-track project is executive produced by both Juicy J and Wiz Khalifa, while also featuring the talents of some of the scene’s very best.
